title: 'GM Street’ — Top 10 Offensive and Defensive Prospects With Mike Lombardi (Ep. 100)
description:
The Ringer's Mike Lombardi and Tate Frazier break down the top 10 NFL draft prospects on each side of the ball (02:00), Dalvin Cook's sliding stock (34:00), the 'Monday Night Football' schedule (35:30), and T.J. Watt ranking higher than J.J. Watt (37:00).
